2000;;Franklin and the Green Knight;;Canadian;;John van Bruggen;;voices Noah Reid, Elizabeth Brown, Richard Newman;;animated feature;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Franklin_and_the_Green_Knight;;Franklin is excited about the coming of spring, because his parents have told him he will become a big brother then. After talking with his friends about it, though, he begins to have mixed feelings. His mother reads a tale known throughout Woodland called The Quest of the Green Knight and Franklin decides to go on his own quest to end the unusually long winter, with his friend Snail as his squire.